{"tid":865454,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"去日本自駕租車 想大家俾下意見","createTime":"2018-10-17T05:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T01:27:25.000Z","uid":2104,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"85fac765b0729cc3ee68ebfdbaf9c8cc9b61965a","tid":865454,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"話說十一月去十日遊中部昇龍道<br />\n會自駕遊 <br />\n以下兩款車係心水<br />\n日產cube Z12<br />\n豐田 Roomy<br />\n<br />\n兩款車都係車仔細細 玩樂型<br />\nCube之前揸過 好得意 又闊落<br />\nRoomy就新車款 1000cc<br />\n<br />\n其實我只係兩個人去<br />\n所以都ok<br />\n大家會點揀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCube<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/133857_fcb026b21f45142831d80101d0834ee9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F133857_fcb026b21f45142831d80101d0834ee9.png&h=c1d9d27f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/133858_8dfc683d0029d753e0d6c4570c212688.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F133858_8dfc683d0029d753e0d6c4570c212688.png&h=e9b77369&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/133859_220b7c0ef5b83cec9cbfcd069dc075e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F133859_220b7c0ef5b83cec9cbfcd069dc075e0.png&h=4ae6d59a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRoomy<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/134132_927c1b5e539249204562fdfe4b3d2fb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F134132_927c1b5e539249204562fdfe4b3d2fb3.png&h=75f8130f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/17/134133_1f3326aab9d495d24f69a2229af84c67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F17%2F134133_1f3326aab9